OL,6,FA convicted rapist who sexually and
OL,7,Fphysically assaulted a woman in a
OL,8,Fhospital toilet has been jailed for
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FLee James Mullen, of Flint, was
OL,12,Fbranded a "monster" for the attack
OL,13,Fwhich happened at Ysbyty Glan Clwyd,
OL,14,FBodelwyddan on 10 December, 2024.
OL,16,FThe 38-year-old had only recently been
OL,17,Freleased on licence, after he was
OL,18,Fjailed for 11 years for rape in 2015.
