OL,6,FThe victim, a woman in her 60s, was
OL,7,Fpunched 30 times during the attack,
OL,8,Fwhich only stopped when her husband
OL,9,Fcame to check on her, causing Mullen
OL,10,Fto flee.
OL,12,FMullen admitted sexual assault by
OL,13,Fpenetration and causing grievous
OL,14,Fbodily harm. Mold Crown court heard
OL,15,Fhow Mullen had been drinking and
OL,16,Ftaking cocaine before and after the
OL,17,Fattack.
