OL,6,FThe court also heard that the victim
OL,7,Fand her husband, along with a friend,
OL,8,Fhad been visiting a friend who had had
OL,9,Fa heart attack that week. Mullen had
OL,10,Fbeen visiting a relative of his own.
OL,12,FThe woman, who cannot be named, read
OL,13,Fout a powerful statement, stating: "I
OL,14,Fwon't let him win." She continued:
OL,15,F"I'm normally a strong lady but this
OL,16,Fhas broken me. I tremble from head to
OL,17,Ftoe at the sight of a hospital -
OL,18,Fsomewhere I'm supposed to feel safe."
