OL,6,FProsecutor David Mainstone explained
OL,7,Fhow Mullen had gone into the gents'
OL,8,Ftoilets briefly before coming out and
OL,9,Ffollowing the victim straight into the
OL,10,Fwomen's toilets.
OL,12,FAs she prepared to leave her cubicle
OL,13,FMullen confronted her, placing his
OL,14,Fhand over her mouth to ensure her
OL,15,Fsilence. He asked if she wanted sex,
OL,16,Fto which she replied no.
