OL,6,FHe then proceeded to punch her '25-30
OL,7,Ftimes', causing her to fall to the
OL,8,Fground, where he then sexually
OL,9,Fassaulted her, Mr Mainstone told the
OL,10,Fcourt.
OL,12,FThe victim's dentures were shattered
OL,13,Fand "she recalls picking up bloody
OL,14,Fteeth from the floor", Mr Mainstone
OL,15,Fsaid. The woman was left with jaw,
OL,16,Fcheek and lip injuries as well as a
OL,17,F"bite misalignment".
OL,19,FJailing him for life, Judge Rhys
OL,20,FRowlands called him an "extremely
OL,21,Fdangerous man".
