OL,6,FBranding Mullen a "monster", he
OL,7,Freferred to his behaviour as "totally
OL,8,Fbizarre, totally off the wall, not a
OL,9,Fnormal way for a human to act".
OL,11,FThe judge also imposed a sexual harm
OL,12,Fprevention order and a restraining
OL,13,Forder both to run indefinitely. He
OL,14,Fpraised the victim for her "remarkable
OL,15,Fdignity and remarkable courage" in
OL,16,Fcoming to court to read her statement.
