OL,6,FHe also commended North Wales Police
OL,7,Ffor taking Mullen off the streets so
OL,8,Fquickly. The victim's husband also
OL,9,Fread a statement. He said: "I have
OL,10,Flost trust in the world. I didn't
OL,11,Fthink people (like Mullen) were out
OL,12,Fthere living amongst us.
OL,14,F"It has impacted so many people in so
OL,15,Fmany ways for the rest of our lives. I
OL,16,Fhave never felt guilt like this. I
OL,17,Ffeel guilt I did not stop him leaving
OL,18,Fthe toilets.
