OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Simon Kneale
OL,7,Fsaid: "I welcome today's sentence, and
OL,8,Fwhilst the lives of the victim and her
OL,9,Ffamily have been irreversibly
OL,10,Faffected, I hope they draw some
OL,11,Fcomfort from seeing Mullen facing a
OL,12,Flengthy detention.
OL,14,F"I'd also like to commend the bravery
OL,15,Fof the victim, along with the tenacity
OL,16,Fof the investigation team who worked
OL,17,Frelentlessly to investigate this
OL,18,Fabhorrent crime."
